OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FA firearms officer who raised his gun
OL,8,Fin the same second a colleague shot
OL,9,FChris Kaba during a police vehicle
OL,10,Fstop told jurors he feared he would be
OL,11,Frun over and killed.
OL,13,FThe Metropolitan Police officer,
OL,14,Freferred to as DS87, was standing
OL,15,Fbeside Martyn Blake when he opened
OL,16,Ffire on the unarmed driver of a
OL,17,Fsuspect Audi car on the evening of
OL,18,FSeptember 5 2022.
