OL,3,CArmed police officer 'feared for life'
OL,4,Cbefore colleague shot driver in Kaba
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FThe blue Audi had been used as the
OL,8,F"getaway" car after shots were fired
OL,9,Foutside a school in Brixton the night
OL,10,Fbefore ` and neither shotgun nor
OL,11,Fsuspects had been found, jurors were
OL,12,Ftold.
OL,14,FDS87 was asked about his thoughts as
OL,15,FBlake opened fire, hitting Mr Kaba in
OL,16,Fthe forehead through the front
OL,17,Fwindscreen.
