OL,3,CArmed police officer 'feared for life'
OL,4,Cbefore colleague shot driver in Kaba
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FHe said: "I have got no doubt in my
OL,8,Fmind, given a moment longer the Audi
OL,9,Fwould have come forward and I would
OL,10,Fhave gone under.
OL,12,F"I felt in fear for my life. Had the
OL,13,Factions not been taken at that point,
OL,14,FI would have died or been injured."
OL,16,FDS87 was the Operational Firearms
OL,17,FCommander in charge of initiating the
OL,18,Fenforced stop with extraction of the
OL,19,FAudi in Streatham, south London.
OL,26,@oD@JOUtD@AOUvD@cO]
