OL,7,FHe was one of three occupants of the
OL,8,F"Alpha" armed response vehicle (ARV)
OL,9,Fthat had spotted the Audi in
OL,10,FCamberwell and began to follow, joined
OL,11,Fby three more ARVs by the time it was
OL,12,Fstopped.
OL,14,FHe noticed the driver was alone in the
OL,15,Fvehicle and that he took an
OL,16,F"unnatural" route suggesting he was
OL,17,Faware that he was being followed.
