OL,7,FThe officer said he took note of risks
OL,8,Fsuch as members of the public and
OL,9,Fspeed bumps on the road before
OL,10,Fordering the "in line" stop in
OL,11,FKirstall Gardens, Streatham.
OL,13,FDS87 gave a commentary on his body-
OL,14,Fworn video footage which showed him
OL,15,Fexiting the unmarked police car behind
OL,16,Fthe Audi.
