OL,7,FHe said he heard "revving" and
OL,8,F"crunching" sounds and the smell of
OL,9,Fburnt rubber as the suspect vehicle
OL,10,Fmoved forwards and backwards to "ram
OL,11,Fits way out".
OL,13,FThe officer was heard on the footage
OL,14,Fto shout "armed police, show me your
OL,15,Fhands, show me your hands" as he
OL,16,Fapproached the front passenger side
OL,17,Fdoor, which he found locked.
