OL,7,FHe told jurors: "At the point of
OL,8,Fcontact on arriving at the passenger
OL,9,Fdoor it was clear the vehicle was
OL,10,Ftrying to make off.
OL,12,F"The vehicle only ever makes a reverse
OL,13,Fin order to have more power to go
OL,14,Fforward."
OL,16,FHe hit the passenger side window with
OL,17,Fthe barrel of his gun in an attempt to
OL,18,Fbreak it and attract the driver's
OL,19,Fattention, jurors heard.
OL,26,@oD@QOUtD@AOUvD@IO]
