OL,7,FHe said: "It is not something you
OL,8,Fwould use in a normal stop. This is
OL,9,Fthe first instance a vehicle has tried
OL,10,Fto ram its way out.
OL,12,F"When police shout 'stop police', we
OL,13,Fusually have compliance. It's not
OL,14,Fsomething I have experienced before.
OL,16,F"Me striking the windscreen was one
OL,17,Fway to get a reaction from the driver
OL,18,Fto see if they would stop, show my
OL,19,Fpresence, to see if they would stop
OL,20,Fbut remove the window."
