OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FBreaking the window would give him
OL,8,F"less lethal options" including using
OL,9,Fa taser and would help him communicate
OL,10,Fwith the driver, the officer said.
OL,12,FIn the footage, Mr Kaba could be seen
OL,13,Fhunched down in the driver's seat with
OL,14,Fhis right hand on the wheel and left
OL,15,Fhand covering his head.
OL,17,FThe witness then ran around to the
OL,18,Ffront and was standing beside Blake as
OL,19,Fhe opened fire.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@UO]
