OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,FDS87 said he raised his semi-automatic
OL,8,Fcarbine at "the same second", but
OL,9,Ffractionally behind Blake.
OL,11,FShouts of "shot, shots fired, shots
OL,12,Ffired" were heard on the body-worn
OL,13,Fvideo immediately afterwards.
OL,15,FDefence barrister Patrick Gibbs KC
OL,16,Fasked whether he had been thinking of
OL,17,Fbacking away from the Audi in that
OL,18,Fmoment.
OL,26,@pD@LOUpD@\O]sD@KOUtD@FO]
