OL,7,FThe officer replied: "Yes, so my
OL,8,Finitial thought was to move around to
OL,9,Fthe front of the vehicle to contain it.
OL,11,F"My next thought was to close down the
OL,12,Fvehicle, the use of the firearm, make
OL,13,Fthe person surrender and not cause a
OL,14,Fthreat to officers.
OL,16,F"Closing down the vehicle as best as I
OL,17,Fcould. As soon as I came around and
OL,18,Fsaw the vehicle was reversing I knew
OL,19,Fit was going to come forward. I was in
OL,20,Fa position I didn't want to be in.
OL,26,@oD@VOUsD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G11/13
