OL,3,CArmed police officer 'feared for life'
OL,4,Cbefore colleague shot driver in Kaba
OL,5,Cstop
OL,7,F"I didn't want to land in that
OL,8,Fposition but I guess training takes
OL,9,Fover and the priority was to contain
OL,10,Fthe vehicle."
OL,12,FHe added: "I had never experienced
OL,13,Fthat level of threat from someone,
OL,14,Fcertainly when pointing a firearm.
OL,16,F"To have no regard for members of the
OL,17,Fpublic or the police in the vicinity.
OL,18,FIt was clear to me even if I have
OL,19,Ftaken a shot, the vehicle would have
OL,20,Fmoved forward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@MO]tD@KOUxD@AOU
