OL,7,F"It was instinct or a way of survival
OL,8,Fto begin to withdraw and get away from
OL,9,Fthe vehicle. It happened so quickly."
OL,11,FThe officer gave evidence from behind
OL,12,Fa screen as Mr Kaba's family sat in
OL,13,Fthe well of the court just metres away.
OL,15,FBlake, 40, has denied Mr Kaba's murder
OL,16,Fat the Old Bailey trial continues.
